NK004(nga)011:0: yum chen mo'i dbang bskur mdor bsdus bzhugs /
NK004(nga)011:2: gang du bya bar tshom bu bkod pa'i gzhir /
NK004(nga)011:8: cha gsum gtor ma rnam kyang bsdogs /
NK004(nga)011:9: rang gi mdun du rdor dril /
NK004(nga)011:12: khrus dang phyag sngon du 'gro bas /
NK004(nga)011:14: tshad med bzhi sgom pa rnams lan gsum gsum dang /
NK004(nga)011:15: byang chub sems khyad par can bsgom /
NK004(nga)011:16: thams cad du yang sa gzhi dag /
NK004(nga)011:17: gseg ma la sogs med pa dang //
NK004(nga)011:18: lag mthil ltar mnyam bee d+aur+ya'i //
NK004(nga)011:19: rang bzhin 'jam por gnas gyur cig /
NK004(nga)011:20: pho brang yid 'ong nyams dga' bar //
NK004(nga)011:21: gdan khri mdzes shing blta na sdug /
NK004(nga)011:22: ngo mtshar mchod sprin rgya mtsho yis //
NK004(nga)011:23: rab 'byams nam mkha' gang bar gyur //
NK004(nga)011:25: chos nyid dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyang //
NK004(nga)011:26: gzhi dang lam dang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen //
NK004(nga)011:27: bdag med stong pa don dam yang dag mtha' //
NK004(nga)011:28: yum chen pha rol phyin ma gshegs su gsol //
NK004(nga)011:29: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri sh+ya ho /
NK004(nga)011:31: spyan drangs pas gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK004(nga)011:32: yum chen mo gser mdog phyag dang po gnyis mnyam bzhag /
NK004(nga)011:33: 'og ma gnyis chos 'chad glegs bam 'dzin pa la /
NK004(nga)011:38: sh+aa ri'i bu sogs sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' mtha' yas pa'i 'khor gyis bskor ba'o //
NK004(nga)011:39: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ga ga na sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h'u /
NK004(nga)011:41: pad+ma +aa sa na tish+tha sa ma t+wam /
NK004(nga)011:43: sarba de ba ta artsi ta a mri ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)011:45: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha
NK004(nga)011:46: ne s+w+aa h+aas sku phyi sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK004(nga)011:47: badz+ra ba sa pe pra tits+tsha s+w+aa h+aas gos zung
NK004(nga)011:48: 'bul / ji snyed su dag sogs kyis yan lag bdun pa 'bul /
NK004(nga)011:49: sangs rgyas bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par shog /
NK004(nga)011:50: sems can thams cad bde zhing skyid par shog /
NK004(nga)011:51: nyin dang mtshan du chos la spyod par shog /
NK004(nga)011:52: rang gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK004(nga)011:54: sku las 'od 'phros 'phags mchod ngan song sbyangs //
NK004(nga)011:55: bdag la phog pas byin brlabs mthu nus thob //
NK004(nga)011:56: gzungs chab la khyab dag byed bdud rtsir gyur //
NK004(nga)011:57: ting 'dzin sgo brgyar 'jug pa'i skal ldan gyur //
NK004(nga)011:58: d+hi pra dz+ny+aa ma h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+harma d+ha tu s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)011:62: badz+ra ar+g+ham pad+yam push+pe d+hup+pe +aa lo ke gan+d+he nee
NK004(nga)011:63: wi d+ye shap+da p+au dza med g+ha sa mu dra
NK004(nga)011:64: s+pha ra na sa ma ye h'u gis mchod /
NK004(nga)011:65: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas gtor ma 'bul /
NK004(nga)011:66: sku'i 'od zer bum chu la khyab pas byin gyis brlabs par gyur /
NK004(nga)011:69: gtsug gi nor bu'i 'od kyis rgyal ba mchod //
NK004(nga)011:70: byin rlabs spyi bor thim pas rjes gnang thob //
NK004(nga)011:71: dkyil 'khor lha las rang 'dra'i sku chad de //
NK004(nga)011:72: spyi bor thim pas sgribs byang dbang thob bsam //
NK004(nga)011:73: de nas slob ma la khrus bya /
NK004(nga)011:74: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad sems bskyed dang chos
NK004(nga)011:75: nyan pa'i kun spyod dang mtshams sbyor ci rigs pa
NK004(nga)011:77: lung a nu yo ga 'dus pa chen po mdo
NK004(nga)011:78: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du chu bo bzhi rdzogs kyi
NK004(nga)011:79: dbang sum cu rtsa drug la /
NK004(nga)011:80: yan lag rag pa brgyad brgya so gcig tu phye nas bskur ba la'ang /
NK004(nga)011:81: sa dang po 'gyur ba ma nges pa nas /
NK004(nga)011:82: sa bcu pa rdzogs pa cig chib kyi bar non par bya ba'i don du /
NK004(nga)011:83: lha ma'i dbang nas brtsams te /
NK004(nga)011:84: a nu rang lugs kyi rdzogs rim mthar thug pa a ta'i bar du byung zhing /
NK004(nga)011:85: lam stegs kyi theg pa rnams so so'i lam dang tshul 'dra rung du byung kyang /
NK004(nga)011:86: don la 'bras bu'i theg pa'i thabs mkhas kyis zin pas /
NK004(nga)011:87: theg pa rang rang gi spang thob dang rigs 'dra'i yon tan de dang /
NK004(nga)011:88: de skye ba'i myur lam du 'gyur ba'i phyi dbang
NK004(nga)011:89: rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor bzhi
NK004(nga)011:90: pa byang sems kyi theg pa'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK004(nga)011:91: ston pa gtso bor byas pa dang /
NK004(nga)011:92: yum chen mo gtso bor byas pa gnyis kyi phyi
NK004(nga)011:93: ma'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba la sogs sbrel
NK004(nga)011:94: la man+dala phul / yan lag bdun pas tshogs bsags pa'i phyir /
NK004(nga)011:97: sangs rgyas chos tshogs lan gsum /
NK004(nga)011:99: slob dpon sangs rgyas dgongs su gsol //
NK004(nga)011:100: bden gnyis don rtogs theg chen gyi //
NK004(nga)011:101: rgyal ba'i mdzad pa mthar phyin pa //
NK004(nga)011:102: zab cing rgya che'i dbang rnams stsol //
NK004(nga)011:104: thog mar lha dbang bskur ba ni /
NK004(nga)011:105: dkyil 'khor gyi lha mar me gcig las gnyis chad
NK004(nga)011:106: kyi rnam par byon nas khyed rang rnams kyi spyi
NK004(nga)011:107: bor nas thim pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK004(nga)011:109: bdag skyed gnyis rtogs kyi yon tan rnam par mi
NK004(nga)011:110: rtog pa'i ye shes khyad par can rgyud la skyes
NK004(nga)011:113: dbus phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK004(nga)011:114: yum chen rgyan ldan rdo rje'i skyil //
NK004(nga)011:115: gser mdog sku ni shin tu rgyas //
NK004(nga)011:116: phyag bzhi dang po mnyam bzhag can //
NK004(nga)011:118: 'gro ba sems can don mdzad pa //
NK004(nga)011:119: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pas bskor //
NK004(nga)011:120: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK004(nga)011:121: d+h+ai pradz+ny+aa ma h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+harma d+ha tu s+w+aa h+aa /
NK004(nga)011:124: sngon byung ston pa'i rnam thar dang //
NK004(nga)011:125: rjes mthun yon tan khyad par can //
NK004(nga)011:126: bskyed byed dbu rgyan yum gyi phyag /
NK004(nga)011:127: seng phrug glang phrug ka shi'i ras //
NK004(nga)011:128: rgyal po'i bka' rtags dbang thob shog /
NK004(nga)011:130: klu rgyal bdud rtsa'i chu blangs te //
NK004(nga)011:131: bcom ldan drin lan bsab pa'i phyir //
NK004(nga)011:132: sku yi dri ma yongs su bkru //
NK004(nga)011:133: skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK004(nga)011:135: ming dang rgyan cha yig shing dang //
NK004(nga)011:136: mda' gzhu btsun mo shing rta chibs //
NK004(nga)011:137: shan gri gseg par na bza' dang //
NK004(nga)011:139: byang sems mdzad pa nyi shu'i rdzas //
NK004(nga)011:141: de ltar byang sems theg pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po yum chen mo'i dbang bskur bas /
NK004(nga)011:142: mdo rang lugs kyi sbyor lam gnyis pa mtshan ma
NK004(nga)011:143: rtags kyi rnal 'byor bslab pa rgyun gyi sa non
NK004(nga)011:144: pa dang rigs 'dra ba'i yon tan gsos thebs /
NK004(nga)011:145: mngon du rgyu yi bag chags 'bring yo dag /
NK004(nga)011:146: sri zhi las rnam par grol ba'i rgyu dang /
NK004(nga)011:147: lam ba dong ma la sbyor ba'i sbyor ba byang chub sems skye ba'i stegs su gyur /
NK004(nga)011:148: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab chen po sa
NK004(nga)011:149: bcu pa'i byang sems kyi rtogs rigs dang 'dra ba'i
NK004(nga)011:150: yon tan khyad par can thob pa'i skal ba can
NK004(nga)011:155: dge ba bsngo zhing slob ma gyes /
NK004(nga)011:156: slob dpon gyis rjes chog mchod bstod /
NK004(nga)011:159: bsngo smon bkra shis spyi ltar bya'o /
NK004(nga)011:160: zhes pa'ang rang gzhan la spar kha'i bcos rim sogs
NK004(nga)011:161: la nye bar mkho bas 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag
NK004(nga)011:162: gi dkyil 'khor las phyung ste shin tu mdor bsdus
NK004(nga)011:163: pa'i tshul du dpal chen 'dus pa rtsal des bldebs
